---
title: Serrano Ham, Mozzarella, Roasted Pepper and Pesto Panini with Herby Fries and Balsamic Rocket
description: This Serrano Ham, Mozzarella, Roasted Pepper and Pesto Panini is bursting full of flavours and makes the perfect dinner night option from HelloFresh. Cook up a fresh start!
